│ information feeding into it.                                                                                                                                                     │
│ Here, the *first transformation* means the *first transformation point* that modifies the IR in the pass regardless of whether it's in the                                       │
│ `autofix/build/llvm-build/106417/bin/opt -p loop-vectorize -S /tmp/reprod_y8r1_0sb.l` module or other modules.                                                                   │
│ #### Opt Information ####                                                                                                                                                        │
